text: Francisco Moreno Domagoso (born October 24, 1974), also known by his screen name Isko Moreno, is a Filipino politician and former actor. He is the 22nd Mayor of Manila since June 30, 2019. He was a candidate for President of the Philippines in the 2022 election. == References == Category:1974 births Category:Mayors of Manila Category:Actors from Manila Category:Living people
title: Isko Moreno
